summary: A cuter version of Jenassa. Replaces her standard face and hair.
descriptionHtml:
[size=+1]Needed:[/size]

[URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168]Apachii\'s SkyHair[/URL] with the additional female hair plugin v1.2 or higher

[size=+1]Highly recommended to get her to look like in my screenshots:[/size]

[URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32986]Maevan2\'s Mature Skin Texture[/URL]

[URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24273]nuska\'s Ethereal Elven Overhaul[/URL] USE THIS! You really don\'t want her to look like she has been dropped as a child...

[URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30]Xenius\' No more blocky faces[/URL] Less edges = moar happy.

[URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30411]Hrvelgelmir\'s Brows[/URL] Good looking eyebrows. Who wouldn\'t want that.

[size=+1]Installation:[/size]

1. Click on \"Download with Manager\"
2. Install

(Did you really need these instructions?)

[size=+1]Loadorder[/size]

Just put it lower than any other mod that changes NPCs and you\'ll be fine, I think.
